## ERB Style (Views)

### Indentation

```erb
<!-- Good: Proper indentation -->
<div class="container">
  <% if @articles.any? %>
    <div class="articles">
      <% @articles.each do |article| %>
        <%= render article %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>

<!-- Bad: Inconsistent indentation -->
<div class="container">
<% if @articles.any? %>
  <div class="articles">
  <% @articles.each do |article| %>
    <%= render article %>
  <% end %>
  </div>
<% end %>
</div>
```

### ERB Tags

```erb
<!-- Good: <%= %> for output -->
<h1><%= @article.title %></h1>

<!-- Good: <% %> for logic (no output) -->
<% if @article.published? %>
  <p>Published</p>
<% end %>

<!-- Good: <%# %> for comments -->
<%# This renders the article form %>
<%= render 'form' %>

<!-- Bad: HTML comments for ERB (will be visible in source) -->
<!-- <%= render 'form' %> -->
```

### Logic in Views

```ruby
# Good: Keep views simple
<%= article.formatted_date %>

# Bad: Complex logic in views
<%= article.created_at > 1.year.ago ? article.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") : article.created_at.year %>

# Extract to helper method instead
def article_date(article)
  article.created_at > 1.year.ago ? article.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") : article.created_at.year
end
```
